  "description": "<p><b>Describe:</b><br/>Protection: This basic protective cover protects your furniture from splashes, stains, abrasion and tearing to prevent damage. It is very suitable for families with pets, or anyone looking for economical furniture protection solutions. Beautify your living room and impress your guests by reducing costs<br/>Lightweight and easy to maintain: easy to set up and pick up; machine wash in cold water, do not bleach, dry at low temperature, do not iron</p><p><b>Product information:</b><br/>Material: Polyester<br/>Size: Single seat 90-140cm, double seat 145-185cm, three seat 195-230cm, four seat 235-310cm<br/>Weight: single 90-140cm: 0.65kg, double 145-185cm: 0.8kg, three 190-230cm: 0.9kg, four 235-300cm: 1.05kg, pillowcase 50g.<br/>Volume: about 30*25*12cm<br/>This is not waterproof<br/>Machine washable<br/>Stretch fabrics</p><p><b>Features:</b><br/>1. Select high-quality fabrics, the sofa is comfortable, highly elastic, breathable and durable<br/>2. Made of elastic fabric material, suitable for most sofas<br/>3. Responsive printing and dyeing technology, healthy and environmentally friendly, not easy to fade<br/>4. Easy to install and separate, just cover the sofa, insert foam in the sofa space, and turn the old sofa into a new sofa in a few minutes.<br/>5. Protect your sofa from stains, pet hair, damage and dust<br/>6. There are 4 sizes to choose from, many colors are available<br/>7. Suitable for home, hotel, office and any sofa needs</p><p><b>Packing list:</b><br/>Combination sofa cover*1</p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/16368480/1636878031451.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/16368480/1636878031939.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/16368480/1636878032043.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/16368480/1